1.1 BAR data

1.1.1 Summary

There are a total of 620 bars included in this study. Sites are divided at three levels across 2 basins. The highest level (loc1) includes 8 large regions including:
florida, caribbean, flowerGardenBanks, northwestHawaiianIslands, marianas, middleHawaiianIslands, pacificRemoteIslandArea, samoa

Within these larger regions are 21 sublevels (loc2) that are generally inclusive of an island including:
keys, saintCroix, saintThomas, puertoRico, flowerGardenBanks, dryTortugas, saintJohn, frenchFrigateShoals, guam, hawaii, jarvis, maug, oahu, ofu, pagan, palmyra, pearlHermes, saipan, tau, tutuila, wake

Most islands or loc2 level includes multiple sites (loc3) within it, totaling 80 loc3 levels across both basins

Deployment dates ranged from 2013-06-19 to 2020-03-06 and recovery dates ranged from 2017-03-29 to 2023-01-11. The deployment duration ranged from 906 to 2373 days and was on 1373.4983871 days.
